382
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:46,039
Very well.

383
00:17:46,279 --> 00:17:47,760
We'll do it your way.

384
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,799
If there are any risks,

385
00:17:50,399 --> 00:17:51,439
